item.title: London Ice Varsity – Imperial retain the trophy
item.author: Maciej Psiuch,
item.description: The utimate showdown between Imperial Devils and UCL Yetis took place last Friday in Streatham. Continuous pressure put on UCL proved to be too much for them to handle, resulting in a crushing 10:3 victory for Imperial. Like many games before, it proved to be a challenge, and victory had to be hard …
